quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  28,29,"Nuko Musa yujuje igihe (bumvikanye), ajyana n’umuryango we (basubiye mu Misiri), arabukwa umuriro iruhande (rw’umusozi) wa Twuri. Maze abwira umuryango we ati “Nimusigare aha, mu by’ukuri njye ndabutswe umuriro; hari ubwo nabazanira amakuru yawo (yadufasha kumenya inzira) cyangwa nkabazanira igishirira kugira ngo mwote.”"
  28,30,"Nuko awugezeho, ahamagarirwa iruhande rw’ikibaya iburyo (bwe) ku butaka butagatifu, (ijwi rituruka) ku giti, (abwirwa) ati “Yewe Musa! Mu by’ukuri ni njye Allah, Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose.”"
  28,31,"“Naga inkoni yawe hasi!” (Arayinaga) maze abonye yinyagambura imeze nk’inzoka (ikubita hirya no hino), agira ubwoba arahunga ntiyahindukira. (Allah) aramubwira ati “Yewe Musa! Garuka kandi ntugire ubwoba, mu by’ukuri uri mu batekanye.”"
  28,32,"Injiza ukuboko kwawe (ikiganza cyawe) mu kwaha (mu mwenge w’ikanzu yawe), kuravamo kurabagirana bidatewe n’uburwayi. Kandi wipfumbate kugira ngo ushire ubwoba. Ibyo byombi ni ibimenyetso bigaragara biturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe, uzifashisha kwa Farawo n’ibyegera bye. Mu by’ukuri bo ni abantu b’inkozi z’ibibi"
  28,33,(Musa) aravuga ati “Nyagasani! Mu by’ukuri nabishemo umuntu none ndatinya ko bazanyica.”
  28,34,"“Kandi umuvandimwe wanjye Haruna andusha kuba intyoza, bityo mumpe tujyane anyunganire, anahamye ibyo mvuga. Mu by’ukuri ndatinya ko bampinyura.”"
  28,35,"(Allah) aravuga ati “Tuzagushyigikiza umuvandimwe wawe, tunabahe ibimenyetso bidasubirwaho mwembi; bityo ntibazabasha kugira icyo babatwara ku bw’ibitangaza byacu. Mwembi n’abazabakurikira muzatsinda.”"
  28,36,"Nuko Musa abagejejeho ibitangaza byacu bigaragara, baravuga bati “Ibi nta kindi biri cyo uretse ko ari uburozi bw’ubuhimbano, kandi ibi (uduhamagarira) ntitwigeze tubyumva ku babyeyi bacu bo hambere.”"
  28,37,"Musa aravuga ati “Nyagasani wanjye ni We uzi neza uwazanye umuyoboro umuturutseho, kandi ni na We uzi uzagira iherezo ryiza ku munsi w’imperuka. Mu by’ukuri inkozi z’ibibi ntizizatsinda.”"
  28,38,"Nuko Farawo aravuga ati “Yemwe byegera! Nta yindi mana nzi mufite itari njye, bityo ntwikira amatafari yewe Hamana, maze unyubakire umunara muremure kugira ngo nshobore kubona Imana ya Musa. Kuko mu by’ukuri nkeka ko (Musa) ari mu banyabinyoma.”"
  28,39,Maze (Farawo) n’ingabo ze bigira abibone mu gihugu bitari mu kuri kandi banibwira ko batazagarurwa iwacu (kwa Allah)
  28,40,Nuko tumufatana n’ingabo ze maze tubajugunya mu nyanja. Ngaho reba uko iherezo ry’inkozi z’ibibi ryagenze
  28,41,"Twanabagize abayobozi bahamagarira (abantu) kugana umuriro, kandi ku munsi w’imperuka ntibazatabarwa"
  28,42,"Twanabakurikije umuvumo hano ku isi, ndetse no ku munsi w’imperuka bazaba bari mu bantu babi"